<lb ed="B" n="0390a14"/><list><item xml:id="itemB27p0390a1401">明杭州淨慈寺沙門釋智源傳</item>
<lb ed="B" n="0390a15"/><item xml:id="itemB27p0390a1501">　燕京法華寺沙門釋德聚傳<note place="inline">祖能</note></item>
<lb ed="B" n="0390a16"/><item xml:id="itemB27p0390a1601">　當陽玉泉山寺沙門釋廣鏔傳<note place="inline">碧潭　靜璽　道泰　悟景　普旺　青普</note></item>
<lb ed="B" n="0390a17"/><item xml:id="itemB27p0390a1701">　燕京廣濟寺沙門釋普慧傳<note place="inline">且住</note></item>
<lb ed="B" n="0390a18"/><item xml:id="itemB27p0390a1801">　潤州焦山普濟寺沙門釋妙福傳<note place="inline">慧印　樂一</note></item>
<lb ed="B" n="0390a19"/><item xml:id="itemB27p0390a1901">　宜都顯明山寺沙門釋道慶傳<note place="inline">妙性　明鏡</note></item>
<lb ed="B" n="0390a20"/><item xml:id="itemB27p0390a2001">　昆明妙湛寺沙門釋悟本傳<note place="inline">淨月</note></item>
