<lb ed="B" n="0390b02"/><item xml:id="itemB27p0390b0201">　通海東華山寺沙門釋慧心傳<note place="inline">真澄</note></item>
<lb ed="B" n="0390b03"/><item xml:id="itemB27p0390b0301">　峨湄普賢寺沙門釋慧宗傳<note place="inline">寶曇　無窮</note></item>
